tags.description: Raninagar Industrial Park was established in the year 1987 in Jalpaiguri district of West Bengal. The Industrial Park is located at a distance of 8 kms from Jalpaiguri Town on State Highway 12A, also known as Siliguri-Jalpaiguri Road.
